data.description: Welcome to your new home! Nestled in the quaint neighborhood of Jordans Crossing, this home offers 4 bedrooms, 2.5 baths, 1800 square feet and a kitchen w/ a spacious island ready for entertaining. The open den is perfect for cozy nights around the fireplace. The large primary bedroom contains a full bathroom and walk in closet and tons of natural light. Outside you can relax or entertain on patio in the fenced backyard that's great for kids, pets, or any outside hobbies. Come and see for yourself and let's turn this house into a home!
